twitter2campfire.rb

Publish a Twitter summize feed to Campfire

feed = any summize feed
campfire = a Tinder campfire object ( eg. campfire = Tinder::Campfire.new app.campfire_subdomain and campfire.login 'your login', 'your password' )
room = the name of the room you want to publish to

usage

t = Twitter2Campfire.new(feed_url, tinder_campfire_object, room_name)
t.publish_entries

The latest entry is cached in archived_latest.txt to avoid reposting.

You'll need tinder, rio and hpricot
sudo gem install tinder rio hpricot

Huzzah.